name: Where Are Those Droidekas?! (V)
Lore: 'When two Jedi are attempting to breach your bridge, even a destroyer droid''s response time seems far too slow.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Scum And Villainy is canceled. Non-unique destroyer droids are deploy -1 and forfeit +1. While all your characters at sites are destroyer droids, opponent''s characters are defense value -1 for each destroyer droid present. (Immune to Alter.)',
